{"tid":429954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又來了！有汗出冇糧出？　沙中線工人堵塞地盤抗議","createTime":"2017-10-09T11:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T03:34:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e72163cb2fc86dd5541b7e83530fa86ba3f633","tid":429954,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中線一批工人，聲稱遭判頭拖欠薪金，多番追討無果，至今午1時許，約10人到黃大仙慈雲山崗村道地盤出入口，拉起寫上「慘、慘、地鐵監管不力...縱容拖糧，拖糧18個月字句」的橫額抗議，車輛無法出入地盤，警員到場調停，聯絡判頭及港鐡了解。<br />\n<br />\n有工人表示，他們主要負責移除及鋪設電線工作，以便興建連接沙中線車站的行人天橋，現時約有10人工作，每人涉款1至2萬多港元，希望港鐵監督判頭出糧，不要讓他們「有汗出、冇糧出」。<br />\n<br />\n至下午約5時，大判派員與工人聯絡後，雙方約定明天再行磋商，工人結束抗議離去。稍後，勞工處及建造業總工會也派員接觸工人，以便了解和跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171009/photo/bkn-20171009153046438-1009_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171009183030\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171009%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171009153046438-1009_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171009183030&h=6a1f0f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171009/bkn-20171009153046438-1009_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171009%2Fbkn-20171009153046438-1009_00822_001.html&d=hAoLjnH3VPVtREvRwMsKRP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5f70c9f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171009/bkn-20171009153046438-1009_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8db7a230efdc9e1ebfe708af61bfea4761b486ca","tid":429954,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"說好的缺人、薪高糧準好前途呢？"},{"pid":"59e4b40230b41de974de91ca0879d0e34de4c608","tid":429954,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有工人表示，他們主要負責移除及鋪設電線工作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有個 電 字，IT類"},{"pid":"91581acb6f266e2453129c3561e3a4e2401097bb","tid":429954,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"none care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2e7b87378d2195eb568792e9ea0912e63def03","tid":429954,"uid":125641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:39:08.000Z","msg":"誠哥都拖糧"},{"pid":"197d5b446dc82cda937a9d4c87d4a25f7749a898","tid":429954,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"似係三沙頂唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462ef9ac25dfa1e0aa93609fca13bf934a8ea955","tid":429954,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"又係放線"},{"pid":"a645c48a97913c51f0b6ca0c1f69531f081c0379","tid":429954,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係放線</blockquote><br />\n電燈佬係風火水電四行中係最撚低賤是常識吧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9891bea3e0451338342932ce008eb5991fc1b3f0","tid":429954,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"返工，不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e096de654628e75c2f9e23fb95c55c4f6e32cca0","tid":429954,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係放線</blockquote><br />\n電燈佬係風火水電四行中係最撚低賤是常識吧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳媒早排吹奏，未見過佢地話下賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34f9bb817962c7f5a65cf150b48a14b861a4690","tid":429954,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工，不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm